---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="About - Synapptiq">
  <section class="bs-container py-24 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="bs-h1 mb-8">About</h1>
    <p class="bs-body-text text-bs-foreground-dark text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Synapptiq is being built by a team with deep roots in clinical informatics, health data architecture, and AI research.
    </p>
    <p class="bs-body-text text-bs-foreground-dark text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
      We've spent years at the intersection of health systems and machine intelligence — running datathons, standardizing clinical data, and deploying AI where it matters most.
    </p>
    <p class="bs-body-text text-bs-foreground-dark/60 text-base">
      More details coming soon. We're in stealth for a reason.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
